Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.70,0:01:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,FOLLOW THE SUSPICIOUS MAN
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.10,0:02:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... just a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.17,0:02:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.34,0:02:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,After he eats enough food\Nhe will get better soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.51,0:02:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know his identity, but I apologize\Nbecause I looked at his luggage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you know where he came from?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.82,0:02:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's huge...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.06,0:03:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.57,0:03:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He waked up! Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.08,0:03:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're looking for work.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.67,0:03:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You travel a lot, but as long\Nas you're physically fit
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,you can do a lot of work,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.51,0:03:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}don't you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is very bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hm?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's wrong?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.55,0:03:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And now well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, what will he do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.54,0:04:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He will stay in our house for\Na while until he gets better.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then where will he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He will find a place to stay if he works here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You don't have to be so depressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My colleagues at work are good people!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't worry, Ian!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.03,0:04:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian Cooper!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is his name!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You chose the man you\Nfound falling in your way?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.70,0:04:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In the future, we will rely on this work!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't he look great in his work?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.58,0:04:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't say it's just great.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if the four vehicles are empty,\Nthey are still made of iron!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He has an amazing power!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,His arms look like they were made of iron!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, Ian!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.45,0:05:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have finished pushing the carts,\Nbring the shovels here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.04,0:05:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shovels?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's in that box near the warehouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought the shovels.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.35,0:05:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You also brought the box?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was very surprised!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No one can carry all the shovels\Ninside the box, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But, he carried the box with all\Nthe shovels! What a rare person!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... um?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That man is much bigger than you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up to this size!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.94,0:06:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We are detectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.14,0:06:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ian Cooper...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.68,0:06:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Carraclough seems\Nto have brought a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we hear some\Nstrange words about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If we rely on him,\Nour work will be much easier!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That man was seen
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,by an employee at the mining office\Nlast week as he was on his way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to be him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Seemingly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.67,0:07:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel it's definitely him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,When we find a phone we will\Ncontact the head office immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.91,0:07:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this car you, Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing inside, really nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle, are you a merchant?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.35,0:07:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Merchant?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There are none other than the wandering\Nhyenas who come to this village in this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked if you were among them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- We...\N{\i1}- Walter!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.34,0:07:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no time to talk with children!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.68,0:07:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a policeman!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.85,0:07:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Something might have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.52,0:07:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}News this evening:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:08:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Last Thursday, a criminal has robbed\NLondon Bank and it's still at large.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The scope has been expanded\Nin England to look for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.93,0:08:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}to solve this serious issue...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- "That's it!"{\i0}\N- Says about a bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well yes... Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thanks, this will help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That man that we talked about\Nbefore was here at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.92,0:08:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I have worked at the police headquarters for 15\Nyears, it's impossible for me to make a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt where he was now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not take an insight into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The police of England
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,must arrest the bank robber!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Bank robber?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The bank robber is in this village?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What is wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the right building!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.41,0:09:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are they heading towards the mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Lassie! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, the store owner said completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.71,0:09:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But there is no light!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is he outside?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,0:09:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just watch!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It's the warehouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:09:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What do they want from such a place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Light was turned on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Learn wisdom from me before uttering any word!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my God, my God, almost extinguished!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You have got a suitable place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.41,0:10:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.83,0:10:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay to live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize because I have no other room,\Nyou can use it as you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,As for the food order,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you can go to Richard's shop,\Nwhich I told you about,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.28,0:10:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can bring it to you if you tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If the purposes are insufficient\Nor difficult, feel free to tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You can rely on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks like the real criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}See you again tomorrow!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't make mistakes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's the real criminal! No doubt about it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,About the Ian's command...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.67,0:11:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so good at the work in the mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.07,0:11:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the truth about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face seems strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something that worries you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.54,0:11:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You too heard the rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact I think all this is nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I too heard those rumors about Ian.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.36,0:11:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But when I heard that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was important\Nto take more care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.83,0:11:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.69,0:11:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's a bit strange...\Nbut that guy is really good!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When I met Ian,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that that person was terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard bad words about him, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,People become more terrified
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,when they talk bad of the others,\Nso they seem to have a lot of enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's painful to misunderstand him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the police officers misunderstood\Nhim because they didn't know him well!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.03,0:12:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But if he was the bank, he really would...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly the police will find the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I will not interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What if Ian is really a criminal...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.30,0:12:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My father will be sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He hasn't moved yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.97,0:12:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He thinks this place is his best hiding place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,In such a simple place,\Nno evidence will be left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you do if you don't\Nfind any evidence against him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.39,0:12:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I will depend on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow I will leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:12:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:13:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, just watch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.68,0:13:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I will set a trap in this city for that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.79,0:13:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good morning, Sam!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good Morning, Ed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good morning, Sam!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Kevin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.17,0:13:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Good morning, Ian!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a really big man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ian Cooper.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he do something bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No, just that London police are looking for
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:14:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,someone who looks like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Can he be a bank robber as the rumors say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that this man\Nhas found a good job here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.54,0:14:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever goes, he will never\Nbe released from prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't mean anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.56,0:14:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Does your husband work in the mine too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I worry about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}John!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.79,0:14:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}John! John!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.56,0:14:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We've agreed to pick up\Nsome berries today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.23,0:14:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a bit busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,John left...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.48,0:14:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.67,0:15:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where he goes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.25,0:15:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,0:15:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:15:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It's you, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where is he going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.11,0:16:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! A knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah-ah ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did the police come to your house as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what they told to my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he really participate in the bank robbery?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we'll be deceived by\Nthe bank robbery, I'm worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.62,0:16:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.44,0:16:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a criminal record!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.49,0:16:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He had to bring that man here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You may be right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.36,0:16:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:17:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What does Mr. Carraclough think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem with my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, John!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.37,0:17:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, I want to talk to you a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.15,0:17:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,About Ian...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian has come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I invited him to dinner because\Nhe worked hard today!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.26,0:17:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It is very delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, because it's taboo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.29,0:17:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ian, do you want another bowl?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.63,0:17:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's up, John?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are quiet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.27,0:17:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.19,0:17:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.12,0:17:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Carraclough, when I left,\Nsomething bad happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.11,0:17:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The manager has lost his golden watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.81,0:17:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Carraclough, that man you brought
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.15,0:18:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is the real thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That man?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Ian!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We have been deceived!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anyway, get out of here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What did Ian do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.98,0:18:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear that from the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.89,0:18:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma Forrest heard about\Nof the strange rumor they had published.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They are here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.33,0:18:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you accuse Ian of criminality?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, leave the rest to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you have any evidence?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We can have you arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you accused Ian being\Na criminal by spreading rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.65,0:18:58.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you do if he is innocent?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.62,0:19:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop from discovering the truth!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.01,0:19:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But stop spreading doubts\Namong the villagers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.07,0:19:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You can come back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.99,0:19:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- Father!\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I have seen him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian had a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, it was part of the luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.43,0:19:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,John, you also have a knife, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.94,0:19:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm the one who gave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.99,0:19:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those people have just\Nlistened to our conversation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.67,0:19:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Quick, after them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be good to be the thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll catch him...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.25,0:19:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm going!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the truth yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.90,0:19:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to trust Ian!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is because he works hard with my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.29,0:19:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be late for school!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Lassie, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Please enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the police come early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hasn't your boss come yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we wait here for him to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You can wait in the manager's office, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.83,0:20:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, what questions should we ask him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.78,0:20:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.43,0:20:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,To do something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.14,0:20:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just close your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.27,0:20:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps the man in the next room notices us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.47,0:20:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.11,0:20:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.06,0:21:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.51,0:21:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not good to forget such\Nan important thing here,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.65,0:21:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,what a terrible man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.96,0:21:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell them we have found the watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.07,0:21:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't tell to the people!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.56,0:21:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However I will inevitably catch him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.69,0:21:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's bad!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.86,0:22:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ian has been arrested!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.65,0:22:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ian was arrested for stealing the golden\Nwatch as the interrogator accused him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.11,0:22:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That guy is not bad!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.29,0:22:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lassie, I'm sure there is something!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.55,0:22:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next episode:\NDETECTING THE INNOCENCE OF IAN{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.49,0:22:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be sure to watch!{\i0}
